text: Sergey Mukhin (born 28 October 1950) is a Soviet equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chișinău
